dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Title on sheet XI. Sheets numbered: Ph. I [thru] Ph. VIII, Parartēma tou phill. VIII, Ph. IX, Ph. X, Ph. IX, Parartēma tou phill. XI. Accompanied by sheet of statistical tables: Statistikos pinax tou Vasileiou tēs Hellados. 1 sheet ; 52 x 57 cm. Historic Maps copy accompanied by index map: Skeletos tou Chartou tou Vasileiou tēs Hellados. Historic Maps copy imperfect: sheet of statistical tables wanting. Historic Maps copy has ms. annotations and hand coloring on some sheets. Gift of the Program in Hellenic Studies with the support of the Stanley J. Seeger Hellenic Fund. Historic Maps copy has ownership stamp of Georges Ducakis, professeur de sciences physiques, 35 rue Kalliga, Athènes, Grèce.
